predictions.article: U.S. agriculture is in crosshairs of China's tariff retaliation
predictions.prediction: If China imposes tariffs on U.S. agricultural products, the prices of U.S. soybeans and grains will decrease by at least 5% within a month due to reduced demand from China.

predictions.article: China Readying Tariff Countermeasures on U.S. Agriculture
predictions.prediction: The imposition of tariffs by China on U.S. agricultural products will lead to a 10% increase in the prices of soymeal and rapeseed meal futures in China within a month.
